description: ATEX Resources Inc. engages in the exploration and evaluation of mineral properties in South America. Its flagship property is the Valeriano copper gold project, which is located in the Chile's prolific El Indio Mineral Belt. The company was formerly known as Colombia Crest Gold Corp. and changed its name to ATEX Resources Inc. in February 2019. ATEX Resources Inc. was incorporated in 1981 and is based in Toronto, Canada.
ceo: Dr. Raymond Robert Jannas Runco B.Sc., M.Sc.
